{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aef0e374bb","title":"为红线女题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"66047ddf12","index":0,"year":1958,"month":12,"day":1,"articleId":"aef0e374bb"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"5f3d999856","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"aef0e374bb","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"红线女，原名健廉，粤剧艺术家。抗日战争胜利后去香港，1955年年底回广州，加入广东省粤剧团。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9489c1c072","type":"title","text":"为红线女\"题词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"aef0e374bb"},{"id":"5f3d999856","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五七年，香港有一些人骂红线女，我看了高兴，其中有黄河。他驾的是他自己，他说他要灭亡了。果然，已经在地球上被扫掉，不见了所请黄河。而红线女则活着，再活着，更活着，变成了劳动人民的红线女。一九五八年，在武昌，红线女同志对我说：写几个「个】字给我，我希望。我说：好吧。因写如右","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"aef0e374bb"},{"id":"a38eaf82f3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"aef0e374bb"},{"id":"1eed5f67aa","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五八年十二月一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"aef0e374bb"},{"id":"69a2b3aba3","type":"paragraph","text":"横眉冷对十天指，俯首甘为子牛。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"aef0e374bb"},{"id":"ad2970c2bb","type":"paragraph","text":"鲁迅","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"aef0e374bb"}],"page":{"id":"d9791a8397","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"aef0e374bb","start":59,"end":59}}}},"__N_SSG":true}